() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ If email sync is triggered, the backend authenticates with Microsoft, fetches) Tj
T*
(    messages, filters likely job mail, parses details, deduplicates by a generated) Tj
T*
(    job_key, then inserts or updates rows.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The code is organized around layers:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ API layer: main.py, routes.py) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Data layer: database.py, models.py, schemas.py) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Business logic: services/application_service.py) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Email pipeline: email_service.py, job_detector.py, ai_email_parser.py,) Tj
T*
(    email_parser.py, email_classifier.py) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. Technology Breakdown) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Python: backend language. Good for APIs, automation, AI integrations, and quick) Tj
T*
(    iteration. Trade-off: not as strong as C# for compile-time guarantees.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ FastAPI: modern Python web framework. It gives route definitions, validation, JSON) Tj
T*
(    serialization, and auto docs with little boilerplate. Trade-off: smaller) Tj
T*
(    batteries-included ecosystem than Django.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ React plus Next.js: frontend stack. React handles component-based UI; Next.js) Tj
T*
(    provides project structure, bundling, dev server, and deployment-friendly) Tj
T*
(    conventions. Trade-off: more JavaScript ecosystem complexity.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ TypeScript: adds static typing to frontend code. Useful for reducing UI and API) Tj
T*
(    mismatch bugs.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ SQLite: embedded relational database stored in a file. Perfect for a small local) Tj
T*
(    app with simple deployment. Trade-off: limited concurrency and horizontal) Tj
T*
(    scaling.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ SQLAlchemy: ORM for Python. It maps classes to database tables and hides a lot of) Tj
T*
(    raw SQL. Trade-off: abstraction can make debugging generated queries harder.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ REST APIs: the frontend talks to the backend over HTTP using JSON. Simple and) Tj
T*
(    standard for web apps.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Microsoft Graph API: lets the app read Outlook messages after OAuth login. This is) Tj
T*
(    how email ingestion works.) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
